               Confined Three Months
            </rs>. <rs id="t18180401-157-verdict889" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18180401-157-verdict889" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 20.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
